Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(353,0)\fnDFHannotateW7-A\c&H213545&\bord2\3c&HA8D3E1&\pos(797.333,246.667)}寶箱怪
